import { Fab, Grid , Typography, Box} from '@mui/material'

import React from 'react'
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import { CcTextField } from '../Stocks'


const Add_data = () => {
// Routes
  let NavS = useNavigate();

  return (
    // Whole Container
    <Grid container padding={6} paddingTop={2} >

{/* Container para sa button paar may padding */}
      <Grid container padding={2}>
                      
        {/* Button cancel */}
        <Fab 
        color="primary" 
        variant='extended' 
        aria-label="add" 
        onClick={e=>NavS("/Mainpage/Invoice/AddData")} 
        >
         {/* // <AddIcon /> */}
                cancel
        </Fab>

      </Grid>

{/* Container for all components */}
      <Grid 
      container
      direction="row"
      justifyContent="center"
      alignItems="flex-start" 
      style={{
        backgroundColor:"white",
        border:"2px solid black",
        borderRadius: 5
      }}>

{/* CONTAINER FOR ICON LOGO */}
        <Grid item md={5} xs={12}>

          <Grid 
          container 
          padding={2}
          paddingTop={6}
          direction="row"
          justifyContent="center"
          alignItems="flex-start">
            <Box
            sx={{
              backgroundColor:"red",
              bordeRadius: 5100,
              height:160,
              width:160
            }} />
            <Grid md={12} padding={2}>

              <Typography variant='h6'> Purchase product:</Typography>
              <CcTextField  fullWidth margin='normal'/>

              <Typography variant='h6'> Date:</Typography>
              <CcTextField  fullWidth margin='normal'/>

            </Grid>

          </Grid>

          

        </Grid>

        {/* Components detailed */}
        <Grid container item md={7} xs={12} padding={2} paddingTop={6}>
          

            <Typography variant='h6'> Name:</Typography>
            <CcTextField  fullWidth margin='normal'/>

            <Typography variant='h6'> Email:</Typography>
            <CcTextField  fullWidth margin='normal'/>

            <Typography variant='h6'> Cellphone number:</Typography>
            <CcTextField  fullWidth margin='normal'/>

            <Typography variant='h6'> Address:</Typography>
            <CcTextField  fullWidth margin='normal'/>       
            

        </Grid>

        {/* Button cancel */}

        <Grid
        item
        container
        md={12}
        padding={2}
        direction="row"
        justifyContent="center"
        alignItems="flex-start">

       

        <Fab 
        
        color="primary" 
        variant='extended' 
        aria-label="add" 
        onClick={e=>NavS("/Mainpage/Invoice/AddData")} 
        >
         {/* // <AddIcon /> */}
                cancel
        </Fab>
        </Grid>

      </Grid>

    </Grid>
  )
}

export default Add_data
